'''國家自由紀念區'''（{{lang-en|Statue of Liberty National Monument}}）是位於[[美國|美國]][[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]、[[紐約州|紐約州]][[埃利斯島|埃利斯島]]和[[自由島|自由島]]的一處[[國家紀念區|國家紀念區]]<ref>[http://www.nps.gov/stli/faqs.htm Frequently Asked Questions] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nps.gov/stli/faqs.htm |date=20170807205159 }}, National Park Service, accessed September 27, 2010.</ref>。[[自由女神像|自由女神像]]就位於國家自由紀念區之內。在2012年10月，國家自由紀念區曾因[[颶風桑迪|颶風桑迪]]的影響而受損<ref>{{cite news   | last = McGeehan   | first = Patrick   | title = Storm Leaves Lady Liberty and Ellis Island Cut Off From Visitors   | newspaper = The New York Times   | date = November 8, 2012   | url = http://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/11/08/storm-leaves-lady-liberty-and-ellis-island-cut-off-from-visitors/   | accessdate = December 1, 2012   | quote =    | archive-date = 2012-11-10   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121110183833/http://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/11/08/storm-leaves-lady-liberty-and-ellis-island-cut-off-from-visitors/   | dead-url = no   }}</ref><ref>{{cite news   | last = Fransco   | first = Angel=   | title = Statue of Liberty Was Unscathed by Hurricane, but Its Home Took a Beating   | newspaper =    | pages = The New York Times   | date = November 30, 2012   | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/01/nyregion/statue-of-liberty-is-fine-after-storm-but-its-home-isnt.html?ref=nyregion   | accessdate = December 1, 2012   | quote =    | archive-date = 2012-12-01   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121201152205/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/01/nyregion/statue-of-liberty-is-fine-after-storm-but-its-home-isnt.html?ref=nyregion   | dead-url = no   }}</ref><ref>{{cite news   | last=   | first=   | newspaper=Star-Ledger   | date=November 22, 2012   | url=http://www.nj.com/hudson/index.ssf/2012/11/statue_of_liberty_and_ellis_is.html   | accessdate=December 1, 2012   | quote=   | title=存档副本   | archive-date=2018-11-16   | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116095200/https://www.nj.com/hudson/index.ssf/2012/11/statue_of_liberty_and_ellis_is.html   | dead-url=no   }}</ref><ref>{{cite news   | last = Mcshane   | first = Larry   | author-link =    | title = Statue of Liberty will remain closed as post-Hurricane Sandy repairs continue   | date = November 30, 2012   | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/post-sandy-statue-liberty-remain-closed-article-1.1211092   | accessdate = December 1, 2012   | quote =    | location = New York   | work = Daily News   | archive-date = 2018-06-19   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619140621/http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/post-sandy-statue-liberty-remain-closed-article-1.1211092   | dead-url = no   }}</ref><ref>{{cite web   | title = After the Storm at Ellis Island   | work =    | publisher = National Park Service   | date =    | url = http://www.nps.gov/elis/after-the-storm-at-ellis-island.htm   | accessdate = December 1, 2012   | archive-date = 2020-01-05   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200105205840/https://www.nps.gov/elis/after-the-storm-at-ellis-island.htm   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>，部分設施暫時關閉。自由島在2013年7月4日重新開放。國家自由紀念區由[[美國國家公園管理局|美國國家公園管理局]]管理。
